bilingual.source: We need a written agreement, not an oral one.
bilingual.target: 我们需要一个书面的而不是口头的协议。

bilingual.source: A written statement of acceptance will not be sent.
bilingual.target: 他们不会单独出局书面的接收函。

bilingual.source: Does the factory have a written QA procedure or manual?
bilingual.target: 工厂有书面的QA程序或用册吗？

bilingual.source: Use of written direct testimony can take several forms.
bilingual.target: 利用书面的直接证据可有以下若干形式.

bilingual.source: Using the written word to express ideas and convey information;
bilingual.target: 用书面的方式表达想法，传达信息

bilingual.source: The idea can be verbal, written in words, or it can be visual.
bilingual.target: 这个想法可以是口头的，书面的或者是视觉的。

bilingual.source: It is usually oral but sometimes it will be in written form.
bilingual.target: 它通常是口头上的，有时候则是书面的。

bilingual.source: Once your ebook is written, ad some nice graphics and a cover page.
bilingual.target: 一旦你的电子书是书面的, 广告了一些不错的图形和封面页.

bilingual.source: Treating your trading like a business means developing a written business plan.
bilingual.target: 对待你的交易像生意一样意味着你要写一个书面的商业计划。

bilingual.source: Do you have a written procedure for handling of hazardous and non - hazardous waste?
bilingual.target: 是否已建立书面的有害和无害废弃物的管理程序?

yingyinNormal.en: Before written history, we had an oral history.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在成文史前，我们有口述历史。

yingyinNormal.en: It's a lot to remember. Well, it's all written down.
yingyinNormal.zh: 要记的东西好多。都写下来了。

yingyinNormal.en: Who did? I'm the hospital Almoner. Nobody's written to me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谁写的？我可是医院司务，怎么没人写信给我。

yingyinNormal.en: That's unacceptable. We're supposed to be given written notice.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是让人无法接受的，我们理应提前得到书面通知的。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, what's he written? I guess he's more of a teacher. Really.
yingyinNormal.zh: 写什么的？主要还是当老师了。

yingyinNormal.en: This is literature? A 2-year-old could have written this. All right.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这也能出版？2岁小孩都会写了 好吧

yingyinNormal.en: Okay you guys, I got a little more written. Are you ready? Yeah. Okay.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好，我又写了一些，准备好了吗？是，好。

yingyinNormal.en: Ooh, guess who's getting an article written about him in Physics Today?
yingyinNormal.zh: 哇哦，猜猜"今日物理"写了篇关于谁的报道？

yingyinNormal.en: Ok. I can do this and focus on my notes. What did I have written down again?
yingyinNormal.zh: 好，我可以的，只要注意讲稿就好,我到底写了什么？
yingyinNormal.videoNameZh: 《公开场合演讲如何展现自信？》

yingyinNormal.en: Wait, wait. Hold on. Sorry, okay, here we go. It is written in Oogway's hand.
yingyinNormal.zh: 等等，等一下，抱歉，好了，我们开始吧。是乌龟亲手写的。

yingyinNormal.en: What's this? This is a code that I've written for our year-to-year projections.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是什么？这是我写的同比数据预测代码。

yingyinNormal.en: I am well aware of our bylaws, Severus, having written quite a few of them myself.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我非常明白所有的法规，其中很多条款都是我制定的。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets》

yingyinNormal.en: In fact, they've been disappointing on everything you've written the past ten years.
yingyinNormal.zh: 事实上，你过去十年写的每一本书销量都不高。

yingyinNormal.en: John, your fellows have attended classes. They've written papers. They've published.
yingyinNormal.zh: 约翰，你的同学上了课。他们写了论文，并且都发表了。

yingyinNormal.en: Mrs. Bing, I have to tell you, I've read everything you've ever written. No, I mean it!
yingyinNormal.zh: 宾太太, 我拜读过你所有的大作。

yingyinNormal.en: I made a written record request 72 hours in advance. I checked the tire pressure on the car.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我提前七十二个小时提交了书面申请，我检查了车的胎压。

yingyinNormal.en: Because thanks to your efforts, a new foundation is laid. A new future is ready to be written.
yingyinNormal.zh: 因为你们的努力，新基础已经奠定，我们已经准备好去书写新的将来。

yingyinNormal.en: China's written history dates back over 3,000 years and through the reigns of over 500 emperors.
yingyinNormal.zh: 中国有记录的历史可以追溯到三千年前，经历了500多个帝王的统治。

yingyinNormal.en: Mycroft told me you'd rewritten your memories, he didn't tell me you'd written me out completely.
yingyinNormal.zh: 麦考夫告诉我你重写了你的记忆，但他可没说你把我彻底删掉了。

yingyinNormal.en: So have you written anything I might have seen? That depends. How much time do you spend on Yelp?
yingyinNormal.zh: 那你的作品有没有我可能看过的呢？不好说，你喜欢逛大众点评网吗？

direction_info.description:
数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全四级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Minutes and seconds are the verbal and <highlight>written</highlight> representations of an uncommon base-60 number system used in ancient Mesopotamia.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 分和秒是古代美索不达米亚使用的一种不常见的60基数数字系统的口头和书面表示。

examination_example.sentence: Number words and their <highlight>written</highlight> forms transform our quantitative reasoning as they are introduced into our cognitive experience by our parents.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 数字词和它们的书面形式改变了我们的定量推理，当它们是由我们的父母引入我们的认知经验。

examination_example.sentence: Before there was the <highlight>written</highlight> word, there was the language of dance.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在有文字之前，就有了舞蹈的语言。
